NextOS port-s7d: clock controller s7d (S905X5M) + DT de boot + GPU panthor.

- clk-regmap.{c,h}: versao vendor (CoreELEC) + clk_regmap_init portado do mainline.
- clk-pll.{c,h}: versao vendor com secure-PLL + meson_clk_pll_v4_ops (s7d usa).
- Makefile: s7d.o + CFLAGS_clk-pll.o -DCONFIG_AMLOGIC_MODIFY (libera v4_ops; no
  arm64 os sub-blocos CONFIG_ARM ficam off).
- Kconfig: COMMON_CLK_S7D.
- s7d.c + dt-bindings/clock/s7d-clkc.h: NOVOS (driver + binding).
- amlogic-s7d.dtsi: nodes de boot (SCMI+clkc+eMMC+eth+simplefb) + GPU valhall-csf (panthor).

X5M-only: o config do device desabilita os outros SoC meson (GXBB/AXG/G12A/S4/T7).

